{"tid":2052472,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國旅遊部:  中國遊客切勿前往澳洲旅遊","createTime":"2020-06-05T14:23:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T03:57:27.000Z","uid":5195,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"61d2d8442115d871e12ea8209c99c74175f72bb0","tid":2052472,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T14:23:30.000Z","msg":"北京當局提醒內地民眾，切勿前往澳洲旅遊；文化和旅遊部在微信公眾號說，澳洲近期受到新型冠狀病毒疫情影響，對華人和亞裔的種族歧視言行和暴力行為現象，明顯上升，內地遊客要提高安全防範意識，切勿前往澳洲旅遊。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲早前力主國際就中國的新型冠狀病毒起源，展開獨立調查，引起北京不滿，先後暫停部份澳洲肉類入口，及對澳洲大麥徵收反傾銷稅；澳洲就計劃修改外商投資規定，若引起國家安全風險，可強制外商退出投資，被指是針對中國企業。"},{"pid":"c9aea3207cd84059c3ef40499d4fa0e8f3d69873","tid":2052472,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T14:24:01.000Z","msg":"歡迎移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451e3374cc2a3baf0089c56f8bf8932416aab86c","tid":2052472,"uid":23684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T14:24:31.000Z","msg":"等領導家屬先過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a393132482ed0ff835f63b61e5b0c3ae6f60bd05","tid":2052472,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T14:24:32.000Z","msg":"排華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ccde694b7b79a252ae1a930bdf912781e5e008","tid":2052472,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T14:25:10.000Z","msg":"有錢嘅都唔會理照去<br />\n無錢嘅就算鳩數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287bb79bfeaf6c5e8e0742c26484ca5f2fca7177","tid":2052472,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T14:30:42.000Z","msg":"澳洲佬遲下一定排撚埋香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3486942849cca2d295961a2985066f801dd4ece9","tid":2052472,"uid":39010,"like":